  • li.mock,

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • li.mvc.AbstractAction (implements li.mvc.RequestMethod)
    • li.service.AbstractService<T> (implements li.service.IBaseService<T>)
    • li.test.BaseTest
      • li.test.ActionTest
    • li.util.Convert
      • li.more.Convert
    • li.more.IocExporter
    • li.mock.MockFilterConfig (implements javax.servlet.FilterConfig)
    • li.mock.MockHttpSession (implements javax.servlet.http.HttpSession)
    • li.mock.MockRequestDispatcher (implements javax.servlet.RequestDispatcher)
    • li.mock.MockServletConfig (implements javax.servlet.ServletConfig)
    • li.mock.MockServletContext (implements javax.servlet.ServletContext)
    • li.mock.MockServletRequest (implements javax.servlet.ServletRequest)
      • li.mock.MockHttpServletRequest (implements javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest)
    • li.mock.MockServletResponse (implements javax.servlet.ServletResponse)
      • li.mock.MockHttpServletResponse (implements javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse)
    • li.dao.MonitoringConnection (implements java.sql.Connection)
    • javax.management.NotificationBroadcasterSupport (implements javax.management.NotificationEmitter)
      • com.alibaba.druid.filter.FilterAdapter (implements com.alibaba.druid.filter.Filter)
        • com.alibaba.druid.wall.WallFilter (implements com.alibaba.druid.wall.WallFilterMBean)
          • li.dao.WallFilter
    • li.quartz.Quartz
    • li.dao.SimpleDataSource (implements javax.sql.DataSource)
      • li.dao.MonitoringDataSource
    • li.mock.Tool
    • com.alibaba.druid.pool.WrapperAdapter (implements java.sql.Wrapper)
      • com.alibaba.druid.pool.DruidAbstractDataSource (implements javax.sql.DataSource, com.alibaba.druid.proxy.jdbc.DataSourceProxy, com.alibaba.druid.pool.DruidAbstractDataSourceMBean, java.io.Serializable)
        • com.alibaba.druid.pool.DruidDataSource (implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Closeable, javax.sql.ConnectionPoolDataSource, com.alibaba.druid.pool.DruidDataSourceMBean, com.alibaba.druid.pool.ManagedDataSource, javax.naming.Referenceable)
          • li.dao.DruidAdapter
